{"tid":1049757,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Microsoft 全面擁抱大灣區","createTime":"2019-03-06T13:30:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T00:18:35.000Z","uid":1886,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7d3e098ee9ca3b9592fddb7576515a3262ba54ac","tid":1049757,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:30:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/53097286_2488775544526542_1088562386043928576_o.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=c92a636699323d0e797b935a59a7ae3f&amp;oe=5CDB4C08\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F53097286_2488775544526542_1088562386043928576_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3Dc92a636699323d0e797b935a59a7ae3f%26oe%3D5CDB4C08&h=229375ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fb.com/itpromag/photos/a.611616738909108/2488775537859876\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fitpromag%2Fphotos%2Fa.611616738909108%2F2488775537859876&d=iefYBA3dMTKG%2BriJzBrQhVScv4UPbHgCWRxxYzHlmUY%3D&h=2d70c051\" target=\"_blank\">https://fb.com/itpromag/photos/a.611616738909108/2488775537859876</a>"},{"pid":"a8e31262f4457bc7229bcc59ae80a9255494ee96","tid":1049757,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:32:29.000Z","msg":"Microsoft 首屆大灣區創新科技峰會 致力推動大灣區數碼轉型<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.microsoft.com/zh-hk/2019/03/06/gba-innovation-summit/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.microsoft.com%2Fzh-hk%2F2019%2F03%2F06%2Fgba-innovation-summit%2F&d=iefYBA3dMTKG%2BriJzBrQhVScv4UPbHgCWRxxYzHlmUY%3D&h=d563c56a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.microsoft.com/zh-hk/2019/03/06/gba-innovation-summit/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://3er1viui9wo30pkxh1v2nh4w-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/prod/sites/424/2019/03/GROUP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3er1viui9wo30pkxh1v2nh4w-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fprod%2Fsites%2F424%2F2019%2F03%2FGROUP.jpg&h=4ff9ab9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">重點培育大灣區科技業界人士   宣佈首個Microsoft x GitHub 大灣區編程馬拉松</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n2019年3月6日，香港 &ndash;&ndash; Microsoft今日假深圳舉辦首屆「大灣區。Microsoft創新科技峰會」，致力支持大灣區發展，推動大灣區數碼轉型，成為全球創新和科技中心的願景。透過雲集超過500名科技業界人士，Microsoft旨在於大灣區內建立一個全方位的合作夥伴生態系統，並藉著Microsoft在人工智能（AI）、IoT、雲端運算和大數據方面的專業知識和優勢，致力推動大灣區數碼轉型。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://3er1viui9wo30pkxh1v2nh4w-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/prod/sites/424/2019/03/HORACE-768x512.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3er1viui9wo30pkxh1v2nh4w-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fprod%2Fsites%2F424%2F2019%2F03%2FHORACE-768x512.jpg&h=b92582ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMicrosoft 中國首席運營官鄒作基先生表示：「大灣區發展一日千里，正在開始別具歷史意義的新一頁。大灣區擁有獨特地理環境差異和多元語言，企業若希望提高營運效率及更有效地與不同城市合作，AI將會是重要關鍵。大灣區將為各大小初創公司和企業帶來巨大的發展機遇，Microsoft一直密切關注和支持大灣區的創新科技發展。憑藉我們在AI、IoT、雲端運算和大數據方面的專業知識，Microsoft 將成為企業高速發展的催化劑，協助大灣區不同行業、公司、合作夥伴、初創企業和技術開發人員，把握非凡的發展機遇，引領香港和大灣區逐步蛻變成為國際性的創新科技重鎮。」"},{"pid":"2fe2a1ef2dbcf83d7040bc071e184c6b2b45fd6f","tid":1049757,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:33:24.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">Microsoft x GitHub 帶領大灣區科技人才發展</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n促進科技人才和資源的交流是Microsoft在大灣區的重點關注項目之一。作為推動區內人才發展項目的第一炮，Microsoft率先宣佈與全球領先的開放平台社區GitHub，聯手舉辦首屆大灣區編程馬拉松。這次編程馬拉松會以AI為主題，將聚集大灣區450多名合作夥伴，提供一個理想的交流平台，以科技連繫參加者的創意和靈感。"},{"pid":"f1408582379aba1d53fe1ebb378a58f500a45c25","tid":1049757,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:35:19.000Z","msg":"微軟（Microsoft）去年收購 GitHub 開發者平台，該公司今日在深圳宣布舉辦 GitHub 大灣區編程馬拉松，會以 AI 為主題,目標聚集大灣區 450 多名合作夥伴，提供交流平台。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2285000/2286588/2019mar06_to_03_1024.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2285000%2F2286588%2F2019mar06_to_03_1024.JPG&h=3abbabb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鄒作基及微軟香港及澳門區總經理陳珊珊在同場上點出該金在大灣區的 4 個發展方向，包括：1) 智能雲端 Azure 平台以及專注於 AI 和 IoT 技術； 2)  推動大灣區產業數碼轉型，加速科技成果轉化；3) 培育新一代科技人才，促進本地科技發展及；4) 建立全方位綜合網絡，加快區域發展和邁向國際的進度。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2285000/2286588/2019mar06_to_04_600.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2285000%2F2286588%2F2019mar06_to_04_600.JPG&h=697f1210&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2286588/微軟Microsoft%20大灣區辦編程馬拉松\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2286588%2F%E5%BE%AE%E8%BB%9FMicrosoft%2520%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E8%BE%A6%E7%B7%A8%E7%A8%8B%E9%A6%AC%E6%8B%89%E6%9D%BE&d=iefYBA3dMTKG%2BriJzBrQhVScv4UPbHgCWRxxYzHlmUY%3D&h=5a0f5a53\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2286588/微軟Microsoft%20大灣區辦編程馬拉松</a>"},{"pid":"ffca07649dd6ffe74ca5dc0f47dea670b80fd55f","tid":1049757,"uid":78533,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:35:21.000Z","msg":"以連登仔邏輯 邊個Microsoft 就係鬼"},{"pid":"c54f14e6e2b668babb02757d139c81ecd241c0ba","tid":1049757,"uid":206895,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T13:36:45.000Z","msg":"不枉我一直都咁支持Microsoft，抵你發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e92afa1e4d388d2815b45bcc6b1f9826d04494c","tid":1049757,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T15:23:43.000Z","msg":"中國microsoft呢？"},{"pid":"c90c2dbc99b23837a62131aec63332da06177ae7","tid":1049757,"uid":55597,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T17:30:33.000Z","msg":"github <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e21d3c364bd054da450bcb6284b3f2965683484","tid":1049757,"uid":111998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T10:39:43.000Z","msg":"中國Azure 同International 通到再講?"},{"pid":"e9ce37977fd2d4b85e9197740f1a6bba91510d65","tid":1049757,"uid":129573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T00:18:35.000Z","msg":"香港老屎忽識撚 GitHub咩"}]}